{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fdc26ff164","title":"关于《毛泽东选集》注释等问题的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0457cbc548","index":1,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":null,"articleId":"fdc26ff164","article":{}},{"id":"f73bdf8dce","index":0,"year":1967,"month":3,"day":null,"articleId":"fdc26ff164","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961-1968卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f1480e95e7","type":"title","text":"关于《毛泽东选集》注释等问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ebf0106e14","type":"paragraph","text":"一、注释现在不要修改，这些人名都不要删掉，这些都是历史。没有司马炎、司马师、司马昭，何以成为“晋史”？","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2a636f4b97","type":"paragraph","text":"二、《关于若干历史问题的决议》写得不好，可以不收。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5fe29b37ec","type":"paragraph","text":"三、《整顿党的作风》中引用刘少奇的一段话没有必要，可以删去。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ea7d61313e","type":"paragraph","text":"四、新印《毛选》，仍用原来的日期。","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f35f0964ec","type":"paragraph","text":"五、《毛选》五、六两卷，一年以后再说，现在你们没有时间，我也没有时间。","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2664387703","type":"paragraph","text":"六、《语录》第二○八页引用刘少奇的话的一段也删去；第二○八页标题“思想意识修养”改为“纠正错误思想”。","index":6,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b51d334b99","type":"paragraph","text":"（1967 年 3 月 16 日，对《毛选》注释诸问题请示的答复）","index":7,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b222cf3db0","type":"paragraph","text":"×××","index":8,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f895cb2ced","type":"paragraph","text":"这是历史材料，后来变动甚多，不胜其改，似以不改为宜。有些注释似可删去，正文不改。","index":9,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cdea7112f5","type":"paragraph","text":"（1967 年 8 月 4 日，对《毛选》出版委员会有关请示的批示）","index":10,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"fdc26ff164","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":570,"end":569}}}},"__N_SSG":true}